data.description: Have you been waiting for the perfect home?  This is it!  Great quiet location in the back of the neighborhood.  Large lot with plenty of room for a pool.  This 2 bedroom, 2 bath home with split floor plan is ready for its new owners.  Tile floors throughout.  Spacious living room with adjacent dining area.  The kitchen features an eat-in breakfast nook, stainless appliances.  Primary bedroom wing includes a walk-in closet and ensuite bath that has a walk-in shower.  Guest bedroom wing has its own bath with tub/shower and closet organizer in the bedroom closet.  A/C 2014, SOLAR HOT WATER HEATER
